      "description": "Little Caesars® has always been the World’s Easiest Way To Pizza!® But with the Little Caesars app, we’ve made the easiest way even easier! Order pizza, pick it up (or have it delivered) and enjoy it. Sure, a simple concept — but we’ve made the process a snap, especially with our Pizza Portal® Pickup, which really amps up convenience! It lets you order online and pick up from our in-store portals. Just punch in your confirmation code and boom, you’ve got your hands on a piping-hot cheesy dream.\n\nAnd if you’re looking for today’s hottest deals, you’ll find them in the app under Today’s Deals. They’re our most-exclusive, online-only offers — and another reason to order your faves! And for those who love a Challenge, Little Caesars Challenges helps you earn our best Rewards by doing what you already love to do: enjoy delicious pizza! So don’t waste any time — download the app and treat yourself today!",
